# Game Store Platform

## Overview
Game Store Platform is a full-stack e-commerce web application developed as a group college project. The platform allows users to browse digital game products, create accounts, log in securely, and purchase game activation codes online.

The project was built using a modern three-tier architecture with a separate frontend, backend, and cloud database.

---

## Features

- User registration and login
- Browse available game products
- View product details
- Purchase digital game codes
- Responsive user interface
- Secure backend API
- Cloud-hosted database integration

---

## Technologies Used

### Frontend
- Angular
- TypeScript
- HTML / CSS

### Backend
- Java
- Spring Boot
- REST API
- Maven

### Database
- Supabase (PostgreSQL)

### Deployment
- Firebase Hosting (Frontend)
- Render (Backend)

---

## System Architecture

User → Angular Frontend → Spring Boot Backend → Supabase Database

---

